1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 19=

3
00:00:20,710 --> 00:00:21,670
(Grateful I met you)
What's going on?

4
00:00:22,640 --> 00:00:23,640
See for yourself.

5
00:00:24,100 --> 00:00:26,070
Didn't I tell you to keep
Qiao Nian under control?

6
00:00:26,190 --> 00:00:27,670
Just sweet-talk her a little!

7
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:29,320
It's only been a few hours.

8
00:00:29,320 --> 00:00:30,760
Now she's marrying someone else?

9
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:32,560
You're useless!

10
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:36,520
Song Che promised her five billion
in funding.

11
00:00:41,360 --> 00:00:43,550
I can't believe I missed it.

12
00:00:44,840 --> 00:00:48,320
I overlooked someone
as important as the Song heir.

13
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:51,600
What do we do now?

14
00:00:51,850 --> 00:00:55,250
We have to ruin this business marriage.

15
00:00:56,430 --> 00:00:58,030
I don't care how you do it.

16
00:00:58,670 --> 00:01:00,560
You must stop this wedding!

17
00:01:00,810 --> 00:01:02,200
(Grateful I met you)

18
00:01:02,200 --> 00:01:03,000
Okay.

19
00:01:10,560 --> 00:01:13,840
(Why does that room feel so weird?)

20
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:18,950
(Luxe Bridal Atelier)

21
00:01:18,950 --> 00:01:19,760
Qiao Nian,

22
00:01:20,430 --> 00:01:21,560
I need to talk to you!

23
00:01:26,790 --> 00:01:27,680
Don't go with him.

24
00:01:29,510 --> 00:01:30,870
We're already divorced.

25
00:01:31,470 --> 00:01:33,830
What right do you have
to control who I leave with?

26
00:01:34,150 --> 00:01:35,870
I haven't signed the divorce papers.

27
00:01:35,870 --> 00:01:37,920
But she has signed.

28
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,560
She's my wife!

29
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:42,350
Enough! I don't belong to anyone.

30
00:01:42,710 --> 00:01:44,840
Whether I marry or divorce,

31
00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:46,640
it's my own decision.

32
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,400
And Jiang Zechen,

33
00:01:48,950 --> 00:01:50,400
we're done.

34
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:52,680
Stop harassing me.

35
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:56,950
Are you really marrying him
for five billion?

36
00:01:59,640 --> 00:02:02,000
He's using that money
to force you to marry him.

37
00:02:02,480 --> 00:02:04,790
He's only doing it for himself.

38
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,480
He doesn't truly love you.

39
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,590
And you do?

40
00:02:10,150 --> 00:02:11,150
From the start,

41
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,520
everything you've done,

42
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,470
which part of it was real?

43
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:20,150
Jiang Zechen, you feel
like a stranger now.

44
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:22,190
It's like I never knew you.

45
00:02:22,870 --> 00:02:24,840
Since college, you only got close to me.

46
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,520
Wasn't it all a scheme you
and Jiang Xiao planned?

47
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,400
I was doing it for your own good.

48
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,400
If the company goes to my dad,

49
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,800
isn't it still staying in our family?

50
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:40,120
Our family?

51
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:42,280
My grandpa built this company

52
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:44,000
from the ground up.

53
00:02:44,200 --> 00:02:45,280
Why should I give it to you?

54
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,360
Let's go.

55
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:47,710
Qiao Nian!

56
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:51,190
If you follow me again,
I'll call the police.

57
00:02:55,910 --> 00:02:57,590
This is one of our featured gowns.

58
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:59,840
It was designed by Wang Feng.

59
00:02:59,870 --> 00:03:01,870
It's a mermaid wedding dress

60
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,960
made with pearls and satin.

61
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:06,150
It was inspired by a girl's
secret dreams.

62
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:08,240
- Qiao Nian.
- Yeah?

63
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,280
Don't worry.

64
00:03:09,590 --> 00:03:11,710
I already told the staff
to stop Jiang Zechen.

65
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:12,840
He can't get in.

66
00:03:13,750 --> 00:03:14,560
Okay.

67
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:17,240
I think this gown suits you.

68
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,590
Want to try it on?

69
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:20,150
Sure.

70
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:22,680
Miss, the fitting room is in the back.

71
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:24,000
You can change in there

72
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,080
and check the size.

73
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:26,520
Thank you.

74
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:31,150
Hello, sir.

75
00:03:31,150 --> 00:03:33,120
What kind of groom's suit
are you looking for?

76
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:36,190
Our wedding will be on a lawn.

77
00:03:36,310 --> 00:03:37,960
We won't have many guests.

78
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,680
Mostly just relatives and friends.

79
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,800
Great. We happen to have

80
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:45,430
a bespoke suit designed
for garden weddings.

81
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,190
You can take a look.

82
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,430
Please follow me.

83
00:03:47,430 --> 00:03:48,240
Okay.

84
00:03:58,750 --> 00:03:59,680
How did you get in?

85
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:03,150
You thought Song Che could stop me?

86
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,520
Jiang Zechen,

87
00:04:05,280 --> 00:04:07,590
I told you I don't want to see you.

88
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,400
Do you not understand plain English?

89
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,800
Qiao Nian,

90
00:04:13,430 --> 00:04:15,310
can you please not marry someone else?

91
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,870
I'll listen to you from now on.

92
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:21,070
You're the one who can't break free
from Jiang Xiao.

93
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:24,190
You chose to be his puppet.

94
00:04:24,310 --> 00:04:25,120
You...

95
00:04:32,700 --> 00:04:33,500
See?

96
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,310
You're just like your fake dad.

97
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:38,070
All rage and no power.

98
00:04:47,070 --> 00:04:48,600
You like betrayal, right?

99
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,390
Fine.

100
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:51,950
Then I'll let you taste betrayal too.

101
00:04:52,830 --> 00:04:54,360
Qiao Nian, are you done?

102
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:56,480
I'm done, honey.

103
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:57,800
Come in.

104
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,770
Jiang Zechen,

105
00:05:04,000 --> 00:05:05,000
why are you here?

106
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,600
I own this shop.

107
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,510
What do you think?

108
00:05:11,830 --> 00:05:12,750
I bought

109
00:05:12,750 --> 00:05:15,120
this bridal brand ten minutes ago.

110
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:20,190
Qiao Nian, let's go
to a better bridal shop.

111
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:21,360
Okay.

112
00:05:39,430 --> 00:05:41,070
Qiao Nian, come with me!

113
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,240
What?

114
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,720
What now?

115
00:05:46,070 --> 00:05:47,920
You know I can't let go.

116
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,310
Why are you so stubborn?

117
00:05:51,870 --> 00:05:53,560
Why can't you let go?

118
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,430
You think what happened before
can just disappear?

119
00:05:57,310 --> 00:05:58,120
Jiang Zechen,

120
00:05:58,830 --> 00:05:59,720
let me tell you.

121
00:06:00,830 --> 00:06:02,360
You can't give me happiness.

122
00:06:02,510 --> 00:06:03,800
Can he give you happiness?

123
00:06:04,390 --> 00:06:06,190
Can he make you happy?

124
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,480
Jiang Zechen,

125
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:10,390
please stop harassing my wife.

126
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:15,720
Get out.

127
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:17,310
Get out.

128
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,390
Did you hear me?

129
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,750
Do you not understand plain English?

130
00:06:27,830 --> 00:06:28,390
Fine.

131
00:06:29,750 --> 00:06:31,510
Then I'll spell it out.

132
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:34,310
You say you love me.

133
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,870
What is love?

134
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:40,000
If you really loved me,

135
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:43,240
you wouldn't force me to do things
I don't want to do.

136
00:06:44,390 --> 00:06:45,920
If you really loved me,

137
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,000
you would know

138
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:52,560
my grandpa and this company
are my bottom line.

139
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,600
Jiang Zechen,

140
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,360
just admit it.

141
00:06:58,190 --> 00:06:59,630
You don't love me at all.

142
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:03,240
You and Qiao Wenjun

143
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:07,720
are only trying to satisfy
your own desires.

144
00:07:11,830 --> 00:07:12,630
Fine.

145
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,240
Since that's what you think,

146
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,830
I'll let you have it.

147
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:41,160
Dear guests,

148
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,870
on the journey of love,

149
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,680
(Bride)
a ring is more than a token.

150
00:07:47,000 --> 00:07:48,070
It is a promise.

151
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:52,390
It is eternal proof
that two destined hearts are joined.

152
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:59,000
Now, please stand face to face.

153
00:07:59,430 --> 00:08:02,390
Look deeply into each other's eyes.

154
00:08:04,160 --> 00:08:09,510
Now, let us witness
their promise of love.

155
00:08:09,510 --> 00:08:12,120
- Yes!
- Yes!

156
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:20,390
Wait!

157
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:33,990
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

158
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:41,870
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

159
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:45,710
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

160
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:49,510
♪Where this ends♪

161
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:56,790
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

162
00:08:56,790 --> 00:09:01,120
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

163
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:04,240
♪Love turns into pain♪

164
00:09:04,310 --> 00:09:08,430
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

165
00:09:08,590 --> 00:09:12,070
♪Yet I still want you close♪

166
00:09:12,070 --> 00:09:16,240
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

167
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:19,550
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

168
00:09:19,550 --> 00:09:24,120
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

169
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:30,430
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

170
00:09:31,020 --> 00:09:35,210
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

171
00:09:35,210 --> 00:09:38,430
♪Love turns into pain♪

172
00:09:38,430 --> 00:09:42,870
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

173
00:09:42,870 --> 00:09:46,220
♪Yet I still want you close♪

174
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:50,450
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

175
00:09:50,490 --> 00:09:53,710
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

176
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:58,430
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

177
